      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 38,
      "message": "This ifelse statement can be simplified eg like this:\n\noverride fun deserialize(\n            json: JsonElement?,\n            typeOfT: Type?,\n            context: JsonDeserializationContext?): InetSocketAddress =\n\n            json?.let {\n                val address = it.asString\n                val parts = address.split(\":\")\n                when {\n                    parts.size == 2 -> InetSocketAddress(parts[0], parts[1].toInt())\n                    parts.size == 1 -> InetSocketAddress(parts[0], defaultPort)\n                    else -> throw InvalidAddressException(\"Cannot parse '$address' to address\")\n                }\n            } ?: throw InvalidAddressException(\"Missing address\")\n\nAlso \"when\" statement is probably redundant - look at the comment about default port",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3081,
        "name": "Jakub Dudycz",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jakub.dudycz@nokia.com",
        "username": "dudini1"
      },
      "updated": "2019-03-07 15:02:01.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
